  "detailed_description": "Azalea is a short puzzle adventure with a cute yet spooky atmosphere.<br><br>Famine has taken the land, forcing you to enter the Forbidden Forest to save your family.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366100/extras/a4b5f1fbcbfdc28f601e35fe9872c67d.poster.avif?t=1604929911\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366100/extras/a4b5f1fbcbfdc28f601e35fe9872c67d.webm?t=1604929911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore snowy fields and dark caverns.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366100/extras/309ca3099bf3a92d0be1edbf5b5d8b45.poster.avif?t=1604929911\" width=400 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366100/extras/309ca3099bf3a92d0be1edbf5b5d8b45.webm?t=1604929911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366100/extras/309ca3099bf3a92d0be1edbf5b5d8b45.mp4?t=1604929911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find and use magic flowers to solve puzzles and defeat bosses.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366100/extras/6a30855b5898073e874cc03d4d8fbd0a.poster.avif?t=1604929911\" width=400 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366100/extras/6a30855b5898073e874cc03d4d8fbd0a.webm?t=1604929911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366100/extra